Class 715 is structured into 15 main divisions:
(A) Synchronization of diverse media
(B) Hypermedia
(C) Drawing
(D) Spreadsheet
(E) Form
(F) Table
(G) Version management
(H) Annotation control
(I) Structured document (e.g., HTML, SGML, ODA, CDA)
(J) Hierarchical control
(K) Layout
(L) Display processing
(M) Edit, composition, or storage control
(N) Font selection
(O) Miscellaneous
